It has over nine billion pores per square inch. Each pore is 20,000 times smaller than a drop of water, but 700 times larger than water vapor — or sweat. This means that rain is kept out while perspiration vaporizes, so you’ll stay dry no matter what.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="grid grid-cols-1"><div class="w-full         {
          "@context": "https://schema.org",
          "@type": "Organization",
          "url": "https://www.gorewear.com",
          "Name": "GOREWEAR",
          "alternateName": "GORE® WEAR",
          "Brand": "GOREWEAR",
          "logo": "https://www.gorewear.com/us/en-us/images/logo.svg"
        }
      </script><script src="https://cdn-widgetsrepository.yotpo.com/v1/loader/SFIdGTmuvdmXOMkfakS48HIWUT0Q67Px7KIwqrxM" data-nscript="lazyOnload"></script><script type="application/javascript" data-nscript="lazyOnload">function setCookie(cname, cvalue, exdays) {
        const d = new Date();
        d.setTime(d.getTime() + (exdays * 24 * 60 * 60 * 1000));
        let expires = "expires="+d.toUTCString();
        document.cookie = cname + "=" + cvalue + ";" + expires + ";path=/";
      }
      function getCookie(cname) {
        let name = cname + "=";
        let ca = document.cookie.split(';');
        for(let i = 0; i < ca.length; i++) {
          let c = ca[i];
          while (c.charAt(0) == ' ') {
            c = c.substring(1);
          }
          if (c.indexOf(name) == 0) {
            return c.substring(name.length, c.length);
          }
        }
        return "";
      }

      function grantABTastyConsent() {
        var abtEvent = new CustomEvent('abtasty_grantConsent', {})
        window.dispatchEvent(abtEvent);
        window.abtastyGrantConsent = true
      }

      function revokeABTastyConsent() {
        var abtEvent = new CustomEvent('abtasty_revokeConsent', {});
        window.dispatchEvent(abtEvent);
        window.abtastyGrantConsent = false
      }
